                     <interp inst="t18220703-24-person261" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the beadle. I received the prisoner in charge with the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw it laying on the pavement, and took it up.</p>
